description: The ImageMate 5-in-1 Card Reader/Writer is a Hi-Speed USB 2.0 Multi-card Reader/Writer that provides the ability to write data to and read data from flash memory without connecting your digital device (digital camera, handheld computer, digital music player, etc.) directly to a computer. USB 2.0 provides superior performance to transfer pictures, music, video and data between flash memory cards and your computer. The ImageMate 5-in-1 Reader/Writer is backwards compatible with USB 1.1 devices and will work with all existing USB ports.
title: Sandisk ImageMate 5-in-1 USB 2.0 Flash Memory Card Reader SDDR-99
